        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How to Use HisabKitab Section -->
    <section id="Usage" class="py-20 bg-gray-100">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-red-500 mb-8">How to Use HisabKitab</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
                Manage your expenses in three simple steps! HisabKitab simplifies your finance management with intuitive features designed for everyday use.
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-gray-200 p-6 rounded-lg transform transition duration-300 hover:scale-105">
                    <div class="text-red-500 text-4xl mb-4">📋</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-red-500 mb-4">Step 1: Register and Set Up</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">
                        Start by creating a free account. Set up your profile with your income sources, preferred currency, and spending limits. Customize notifications to stay updated.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-200 p-6 rounded-lg transform transition duration-300 hover:scale-105">
                    <div class="text-red-500 text-4xl mb-4">📝</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-red-500 mb-4">Step 2: Record Expenses</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">
                        Log your daily expenses in various categories like food, utilities, and entertainment. Add notes, set reminders, and track where your money is going.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-200 p-6 rounded-lg transform transition duration-300 hover:scale-105">
                    <div class="text-red-500 text-4xl mb-4">📊</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-red-500 mb-4">Step 3: Analyze and Improve</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">
                        Review detailed reports, charts, and summaries. Use insights to adjust your budget, cut unnecessary spending, and improve your financial habits.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-12">With HisabKitab, tracking expenses has never been easier. Take control of your finances today!</p>
        </div>
    </section>

